Package userinterface

Class SaveDialog

java.lang.Object
userinterface.AbstractFrame
userinterface.GenericDialogScreen
userinterface.SaveDialog
public class SaveDialog
extends GenericDialogScreen
A class to represent a dialog that is shown when the user wants to savej a page loaded in the Browsr application.

The dialog asks for a Name and URL value of the page to be saved, along with providing two UIButton's: one to save the page and one to cancel the saving action.
